-- China Provides 5.5 Billion Yuan in Subsidies for Auto Sales in Rural Areas
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-16T10:02:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/china-provides-5-5-billion-yuan-in-subsidies-for-auto-sales-in-rural-areas.html

          
          
             China paid out 5.5 billion yuan in
subsidies for auto sales in rural areas in the first half of
this year and gave 2.4 billion yuan of subsidies for motocycle
sales, the Ministry of Commerce said in a statement posted on
its website today.  
